      "utterance": "最后确认各节点的业务映射：USER是CustomerLoyalty入口，R53是OrderManagement的DNS，EDGE/LAMBDA/CERT/CACHE都属于Inventory层，OAI和FILES属于OrderManagement的存储。这个对应关系要准确。",
